{"tid":491023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門被歐盟列避稅天堂黑名單 憂隨時被制裁","createTime":"2017-12-06T06:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T08:53:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8a51742797e3122c3af9fc882e5c59ff017b90","tid":491023,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171206/20236561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F20236561&d=06gfd3pA%2Fau4FvtBh%2FCmGqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7b71c02c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F20236561&h=75ad9bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171206/20236561</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門被歐盟列避稅天堂黑名單<br />\n憂隨時被制裁<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐盟財長周二通過避稅天堂黑名單，名單中包括17個國家及地區，指這些國家在稅務問題上並不合作，而澳門亦榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n17個避稅天堂除澳門外，包括美屬薩摩亞、巴林、格林納達、關島、南韓、馬紹爾群島、蒙古、納米比亞、帕勞、巴拿馬、聖盧西亞、薩摩亞、特立尼達和多巴哥、突尼斯和阿聯酋，被列入黑名單的國家可能會受到制裁。<br />\n<br />\n法國財長勒梅爾（Bruno Le Maire）表示，另有47個國家或地區列入「灰名單」，這些國家或地區目前不遵守歐盟的規定，但承諾會修改其稅務條例。<br />\n<br />\n隨著多次離岸避稅天堂事件曝光，歐盟成員國今年二月宣佈推出黑名單，以打擊公司及富豪成立海外空殼公司。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"97f88b010b7c3535697ce2c675607c1f5f2b6ab0","tid":491023,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"竟然無香港算好俾面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2662e33ec0b1c89caa6341b65651cb429e32dc","tid":491023,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然無香港算好俾面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHSBC 一向定期交罰款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a5d1ece52a6ae83f4fe84e215ca55ac0b1ec53","tid":491023,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"冇香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0527e29e3d8202c4066d502e794f4fa05fb4d95","tid":491023,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"摩洛哥、百慕達呢"},{"pid":"f63a40b1f93fa7e89e57049f4ec47ee53b2ab93c","tid":491023,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摩納哥、百慕達呢</blockquote>"}]}